## Welcome!

This is the setup chapter. Complete the steps below and run `./<% .Slug %> check` to get started.

## Steps

1. Make sure you have all prerequisites installed
2. Download the workshop binary (or build from source with `go build -o <% .Slug %> .`)
3. Run the workshop: `./<% .Slug %> serve --open`

{{< details "Hint" >}}
Run `./<% .Slug %> status` to see which chapters are unlocked.
{{< /details >}}

{{< details "Solution" >}}
Once your setup checks pass, run `./<% .Slug %> check` to unlock the next chapter.
{{< /details >}}
